GuideCfg.Describe: <color=#622b2b>Welcome to my garden</c>
<color=#622b2b>Next</c><outline color=#3d240a width=1><color=#46f700>Click</c></outline><color=#622b2b>to start the battle</c>
<outline color=#3d240a width=1><color=#46f700>Long press and drag</c></outline><color=#622b2b>The plant can be placed on the lawn</c>

<color=#622b2b>Placing plants will</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>consume sunlight</c></outline><color=#622b2b>and</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>placement quantity</c></outline><color=#622b2b></c>
<color=#622b2b>Again</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>Drag</c></outline><color=#622b2b>Plants can undergo plant evolution</c>
The evolved plant properties will become stronger</c>
Nut strength can resist the vast majority of zombies</c>
Let's start the battle</c>
<color=#622b2b>Now let's have a</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>lottery</c></outline><color=#622b2b></c>
<color=#622b2b>Extract</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>Excess fragments</c></outline><color=#622b2b>that can be used to upgrade plants</c>
<color=#622b2b>View more plant evolution paths in the illustrated guide</c>
<color=#622b2b>Huh? We just received an</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>equipment</c></outline><color=#622b2b>, go and take a look</c>

<color=#622b2b>Bob is wearing</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>weapons</c></outline><color=#622b2b>. After that, he can also go to battle</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700></c></outline><color=#622b2b></c>
<color=#622b2b>Now, try installing the weapon you just obtained</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700></c></outline><color=#622b2b></c>
<color=#622b2b>Great, now Bob can also help in</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>battles</c></outline><color=#622b2b>! Go and give it a try</c>
<color=#622b2b>Different weapons have different</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>Attack effect&cooldown time</c>

<color=#622b2b>Below the character,</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>When the progress bar is full</c></outline><color=#622b2b>,</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>Click anywhere on the screen</c></outline><color=#622b2b>to beat zombies</c>
Now? Crush them!

<color=#622b2b>I heard that</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>Cemetery lottery</c></outline><color=#622b2b>It's easier to get</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>High quality equipment</c></outline>Oh</c>
<color=#622b2b>Great! Got new equipment, don't forget to</c><outline color=#3d240a width=4><color=#46f700>Wear</c></outline><color=#622b2b>on</c>
